<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>个人自我介绍</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .profile-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 5px solid #e8f0fe;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .info-section {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .info-item span {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
            width: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #e8f0fe;
            border-radius: 50%;
            line-height: 40px;
            color: #3498db;
            margin: 0 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .social-links a:hover {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
        }
        /* 响应式适配 */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .profile-card {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            .avatar {
                width: 140px;
                height: 140px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .info-item span {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-card">
            <!-- 头像区域 -->
            <img src="IMG-20250420-WA0023.jpg" alt="个人头像" class="avatar" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/180';this.alt='默认头像'">
            
            <!-- 基本信息 -->
            <h1>你的名字</h1>
            <div class="title">你的职业/身份（如：产品设计师 | 前端开发工程师）</div>
            
            <!-- 个人简介 -->
            <p class="intro-text">
                你好！我是一名[职业领域]从业者，拥有[X年]相关经验，擅长[核心技能1]、[核心技能2]和[核心技能3]。
                热爱[兴趣方向，如：技术探索/创意设计/用户体验优化]，始终保持对新鲜事物的好奇心，
                希望通过专业能力为[目标领域，如：产品创新/项目落地/团队成长]贡献价值。
            </p>
            
            <!-- 详细信息 -->
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-item"><span>所在城市：</span>你的城市</div>
                <div class="info-item"><span>联系邮箱：</span>your-email@example.com</div>
                <div class="info-item"><span>核心技能：</span>[技能1]、[技能2]、[技能3]</div>
                <div class="info-item"><span>兴趣爱好：</span>[爱好1]、[爱好2]、[爱好3]</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 社交链接（可替换为自己的链接） -->
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" title="GitHub">G</a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/" target="_blank" title="LinkedIn">L</a>
                <a href="https://weixin.qq.com/" target="_blank" title="微信">W</a>
                <a href="https://blog.example.com/" target="_blank" title="博客">B</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
